On March 15, 2024, Duke Energy Corporation (the &#8220;Corporation&#8221;) announced that Mr. Harry K. Sideris has been appointed as President, effective April 1, 2024. Mr. Sideris, age 53, has served as Executive Vice President, Customer Experience, Solutions and Services since May 2021. From October 2019 to May 2021, he served as Senior Vice President, Customer Experience and Services, and from June 2018 to October 2019 he served as Senior Vice President, Chief Distribution Officer. Prior to that he served in various other leadership positions, including State President, Florida, since joining the Corporation and its predecessors in 1996.

